datetime=\"2016-04-01T05:12:20+00:00\">April 1, 2016</time></div>                            </div>\n\n\n            <div class=\"td-excerpt\">\n                Kuk (yoke) adalah kayu balok dimana biasanya diletakkan pada bagian atas leher sapi maupun kerbau sebagai alat yang bisa membantu kerjasama sepasang hewan tersebut...            </div>\n\n            \n        </div>\n\n        \n\t</div> <!-- ./td-block-span4 -->\n\n\t<div class=\"td-block-span4\">\n\n        <div class=\"td_module_2 td_module_wrap td-animation-stack\">\n            <div class=\"td-module-image\">\n                <div class=\"td-module-thumb\"><a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/wayang-babad/702/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Wayang Babad\"><img width=\"316\" height=\"160\" class=\"entry-thumb\" src=\"https://www.plengdut.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Harya-Panangsang-Wayang-Dupara-316x160.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"Wayang Babad\"></a></div>                <a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/kamus/seni-dan-budaya/\" class=\"td-post-category\">Seni Dan Budaya</a>            </div>\n            <div class=\"entry-title td-module-title\"><a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/wayang-babad/702/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Wayang Babad\">Wayang Babad</a></div>\n\n            <div class=\"td-module-meta-info\">\n                <div class=\"td-post-author-name\"><a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/author/plengdut/\">Plengdut</a> <span>-</span> </div>                <div class=\"td-post-date\"><time class=\"entry-date updated td-module-date\" datetime=\"2013-02-10T05:11:00+00:00\">February 10, 2013</time></div>                            </div>\n\n\n            <div class=\"td-excerpt\">\n                \nSalain wayang Purwa, Madya, dan Gedog, para seniman Indonesia umumnya dan seniman Jawa khususnya telah menciptakan berbagai wayang baru yang pementasannya bersumber pada cerita-cerita...            </div>\n\n            \n        </div>\n\n        \n\t</div> <!-- ./td-block-span4 -->\n\n\t<div class=\"td-block-span4\">\n\n        <div class=\"td_module_2 td_module_wrap td-animation-stack\">\n            <div class=\"td-module-image\">\n                <div class=\"td-module-thumb\"><a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/silsilah-abiyasa/666/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Silsilah Abiyasa\"><img width=\"324\" height=\"160\" class=\"entry-thumb\" src=\"https://www.plengdut.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Silsilah-Abiyasa-324x160.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"Silsilah Abiyasa\"></a></div>                <a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/kamus/seni-dan-budaya/\" class=\"td-post-category\">Seni Dan Budaya</a>            </div>\n            <div class=\"entry-title td-module-title\"><a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/silsilah-abiyasa/666/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Silsilah Abiyasa\">Silsilah Abiyasa</a></div>\n\n            <div class=\"td-module-meta-info\">\n                <div class=\"td-post-author-name\"><a href=\"https://www.plengdut.com/author/plengdut/\">Plengdut</a> <span>-</span> </div>                <div class=\"td-post-date\"><time class=\"entry-date updated td-module-date\" datetime=\"2013-02-18T06:22:00+00:00\">February 18, 2013</time></div>                            </div>\n\n\n            <div class=\"td-excerpt\">\n                \n\n\nSilsilah Abiyasa || (Sumber: Buku Pratiwimba Adiluhung, Sejarah dan Perkembangan\nWayang, hal 283, 1988).\n\n\n\n\n            </div>\n\n            \n        </div>\n\n        \n\t</div> <!-- ./td-block-span4
